4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. In just 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. They will also learn to create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course includes real-life case studies and hands-on practice to prepare students for their future careers. The classes are taught in either English or Spanish, and the course is available both online and in-person. With small class sizes (maximum 12 people), students can receive personalized attention. Upon completion of the course, students will receive a recognized certificate. More information can be found on the 4Geeks Academy website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). Stop.